text: Yacoub Romanos (17 May 1935 - 24 August 2011) was a Lebanese wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman middleweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1935 births Category:2011 deaths Category:Lebanese male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Lebanon Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Batroun District
